{
  "stem": "14292.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, my brother is still the-- my brother-- we will probably talk about this later-- because he-- we were Jewish, we could not go to the university.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The university had, in Hungary, so-called numerus clausus. 'Numerus clausus' is a Latin word for exclusion by number.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was a very limited number of Jews could go to the university.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he was always very interested in engineering.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my parents were able to send him to Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So during-- he was studying in Zurich, which was at that time in Europe one of the best-known engineering schools-- still is in Europe.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was there, fortunately, during the whole period, which was very fortunate because his age group of individuals who stayed in Hungary mostly were killed or taken to camps, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Did you learn German, too?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we learned-- we learned Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We learned German.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We learned French.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And first of all, we learned Latin.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, well, and naturally, [LAUGHS] Hungarian, I think.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was really structured very much around the work of my parents, naturally.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were very much-- expected us to be available.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so we had a very precise schedule.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My mother, in the-- during the weekdays, after they take a-- the eating, she took a half-hour nap.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so we were eating at 1 o'clock very precisely and 7 o'clock in the evening.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was the-- then, of course, we had to study, which, at that time, I didn't enjoy too much.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And on-- my grandfather actually had a-- built a little on-- I wouldn't say a synagogue, because that was invading a building.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But it was a place when Jewish people congregated and prayed, actually even during the holidays, which was very close by.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
